\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi mom post 狗"},{"pid":"28bfa7aed398d5ae01d5179c3ec61ca42999d8c0","tid":1801991,"uid":343059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d9a203ae034ba4513c122f53e0e76f1e6532158","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28bfa7aed398d5ae01d5179c3ec61ca42999d8c0","tid":1801991,"uid":343059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff7ce14ee87ddea32fee4731b571e52243c2772","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"<em>(長文)今時今日我d中同竟然仲可以同警甴朋友玩...</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801886</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完依個post 有感而發<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">社交排斥警犬 <br />\n根本就係係最無成本最簡單，必須要做嘅事</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n連登仔應該大多都18至22歲 <br />\n你嘅中同 大同 一齊長大嘅朋友 <br />\n相信仲會有一兩個係做咗警犬 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">然後你哋可能會覺得</span><br />\n- 一齊大 識佢咁耐 佢唔會打人嘅<br />\n- 清楚知道佢唔係咁嘅人<br />\n- 佢都係打份工 屋企又有經濟壓力<br />\n- 佢岩岩先出學堂 佢好純架 又有抱負<br />\n又或者 真係十年兄弟 唔想無咗依個朋友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">但我同你講 唔係咁 都唔好合理化 佢哋行為</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 由佢哋班狗矇面個日 到無顯示身分號碼開始起 <br />\n再沒有所謂嘅白警</span><br />\n<br />\n因為 紀律部隊係一team人 一個unit 無單獨可言性<br />\n你諗下你睇過嘅電視 電影 當有人做錯 係全隊受罰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>然後佢哋選擇蓋過佢哋嘅編號</strong><br />\n<strong>就代表佢哋所有人更加共同承擔同承認所做嘅行為</strong></span><br />\n如果有白警 一係一早踢爆 一係一早辭咗職<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 諗下犧牲咗嘅人 受過暴力嘅人 <br />\n同因濫暴 面臨刑責 可能會失去自由嘅人<br />\n</span><br />\n6000位被捕人仕 48小時嘅精神煎熬<br />\n300人面臨失去十年嘅光陰<br />\n以千位計嘅屍體發現 同 自殺案件<br />\n周同學嘅離去<br />\n20多位以死相諫嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果仲同警犬係朋友，你哋對唔對得住佢哋？</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2308b70e03d0c11c3a2d5efab07fcdbe89c5a556","tid":1801991,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"038ae7fc31d10f5bfa8e11d48eec357692bbab29","tid":1801991,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"【第拾玖期牆紙】毋懼強權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9b01bed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqcF6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqcF6Fe.jpg&h=44c58009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4045cca7e1ad81f2341681b39fc1a9b21784ae33","tid":1801991,"uid":139578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"認同 推"},{"pid":"4aa674e710e72c722f5fb08eafd83747aa30dfc5","tid":1801991,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"7b41f853a05002108ad0e78ff68edce4b1943f4a","tid":1801991,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04de968449bf490f1dc2a87be5ca62b1cc361872","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4045cca7e1ad81f2341681b39fc1a9b21784ae33","tid":1801991,"uid":139578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"認同 推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c6e8308e305c2214132cbc736aa5c640773e588","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa674e710e72c722f5fb08eafd83747aa30dfc5","tid":1801991,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aa2e42fe850aab9fe1f85c08e31f4f1537e07ab","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4496929dffba15851cb6f4f926ecfe3073a634a","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7295f5dc3b7c73c6f5f75b803d3709b8a1ee75e","tid":1801991,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"死黑狗屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56184b2d8f775338ddc975961149fbb197e20413","tid":1801991,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a875e01d000d9b9b5e642945c932633601eff96","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"姐係14年我大學時 經歷雨傘<br />\n當時嘅中同一樣有走出黎<br />\n然後2年後佢為咗所謂嘅生活<br />\n考上警犬<br />\n最後聽其他中同講 <br />\n佢對市民嘅不滿 係最多 最憎恨我哋<br />\n<br />\n然後 我所識嘅 仲做梗狗嘅<br />\n佢哋身邊嘅人<br />\n一樣有人參加佢地班狗嘅婚禮<br />\n一樣有一大班人會同班狗夫婦去野餐<br />\n一樣有班中同 同兩隻狗 去旅行<br />\n一樣有班人 同隻狗 晚聚<br />\n<br />\n但我想帶出嘅係<br />\n如果你哋口叫 &lsquo;光復香港 時代革命&rdquo;<br />\n平時去一過有不反嘅集會 遊行都覺得自己已經做得好多<br />\n然後只係投個票 再食個黃店就覺得係贖罪卷<br />\n可唔可以只少唔好咁偽善到<br />\n依然同班狗做朋友<br />\n對於犧牲咗嘅人 你哋對得住佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光環同大愛撚 唔係各打50大板就無事啊<br />\n佢哋係錯就係錯<br />\n價值觀都錯到咁嘅人<br />\n點解仲要同佢哋fd落去<br />\n由班狗同狗 互相舔傷口 互相慰藉啦好嘛</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"agree!<br />\n#boycottpopo"},{"pid":"c3bed9f78a2cc791035cbe78334a7c5ae5779284","tid":1801991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56184b2d8f775338ddc975961149fbb197e20413","tid":180199